quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  7,109,"Nhemfo {anaa mpanimfoͻ} a wͻn wͻ Farao nkorͻfoͻ no mu no kaa sε: “Nokorε sε, woi yε nkoyaayini a onim de (anaasε waben)"
  7,110,Ɔpε sε otu mo fri mo asaase no soͻ; na modwen ho sεn?”
  7,111,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Ma no ne onua no nwͻ hͻ, (anaa wͻ’ntwεn) na soma dawubͻfoͻ wͻ nkuro no so (ma wͻnkͻ boaboa nkonyaayifoͻ ano)"
  7,112,Wͻ’de nkonyaayifoͻ a wͻ’nim de (anaasε w’aben) biara bεberε wo”
  7,113,"Nkonyaayifoͻ no baa Farao hͻ no, wͻ’kaa sε: “Sε εba sε yε’di nkonim a yεbenya akatua paa“"
  7,114,"Farao kaa sε: “Aane! (Sε modi nkonim a) mobεka wͻn a wͻ’bεn (me) no ho “"
  7,115,"(Nkonyaayifoͻ no) kaa sε: “Mose, wo na wo (bεdi kan) atoͻ anaa yεn na (yeni kan) ntoͻ?”"
  7,116,"Mose kaa sε: “ Monto. ”Ɛberε a wͻ’toeε no wͻ’brii amanfoͻ no aniso, na wͻ’bͻͻ ehuu guu wͻn mu, na wͻ’yii nkonyaa kεseε paa adi"
  7,117,"Yeyi kyerεε Mose sε: “Fa wo poma no to hᴐ.” Na hwε, εmemenee wͻn nkontompo deε (a wͻ’yi kyerεeε no nyinaa)"
  7,118,"Enti nokorε no sii pi, na deε na wͻ’yε no yεε kwa"
  7,119,"(Farao nkorͻfoͻ no) dii nkoguo wͻ hͻ, na wͻ’de animguaseε san wͻn akyi (kͻe)"
  7,120,Nkonyaayifoͻ no de wͻn ho kͻͻ fͻm de wͻn anim butuu fͻm
  7,121,"Kaa sε: “Y’agye Abͻdeε nyinaa Wura Nyankopͻn no adi"
  7,122,Mose ne Aaron Wura Nyankopͻn no
  7,123,"Farao kaa sε: “Moagye no adi wͻ aberε a menya mmaa mo ho kwan? Woi yε εpͻ a moabͻ no wͻ kuro yi ho sε, mobetu emu foͻ no. Mobehunu seesei ara"
  7,124,"Sԑ ԑteԑ biara metwitwa monsa ne monan abͻ no abira, na m’asan abͻ mo nyinaa asennua mu.”"
  7,125,"(Farao nkonyaayifoͻ a wͻ’agye Mose adie no) kaa sε: “Nokorε sε, ye’Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ na yε’bεsan akͻ"
  7,126,"Deε enti wode bɔne retua yɛn ka ara ne sε, εberε a ye’Wura Nyankopͻn nsεnkyerεnee baa yεn hͻ no y’agye adi nti. “Ye’Wura Nyankopͻn (yεsrε Wo sε), hwie aboterε gu yεn so na ma yεn nwu sε Muslimifoͻ”"